cat << EOF
TUTOS (The Ultimate Team Organization Software) is a groupware or ERP/CRM suite
that helps small to medium teams manage various things in one place. Features:
* a calendar for users and groups
* Groups / Teams
* address manager for people, companies and departments
* bug tracking system
* product/project repository
	o with task management
	o with document management
	o with installation management
	o support of different roles (manager,developer,customer etc.)
	o support of relations to other projects (base product, subproject etc.)
* mailboxes (imap/pop)
* timetracking on projects, installations and bugs
* Invoices
* Watchlists. Stay informed on changes on projects/bugs etc via email.
* support for teams that are distributed over different timezones
* color schemes
* fine grained permission handling
* change history
EOF
